{"tid":1975314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍：區議員「食人血饅頭，連汁都舔埋」「除了仇警，只有仇警」","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T16:25:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c8558d7439ac9c4434981fca9e1c69f26f9d16","tid":1975314,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會通過重組警隊議案 警批食人血饅頭<br />\n16.04.2020 20:20<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議會通過「重組警隊，停止濫暴」議案，民政專員余健強和警方代表在討論期間離席，區議會在無秘書支援下，亦通過臨時動議，計劃向廉政公署舉報余健強涉嫌公職人員行為失當。<br />\n<br />\n油尖警區指揮官林鴻釧在離場前指，議案內容失實，「除了仇警，只有仇警」，強調警隊是香港治安的第一道和最後一道防線，反而暴徒暴行是鐵證如山，批評區議員為暴力抬轎，「食人血饅頭，連汁都舔埋」，坐享政治紅利，又指很多年輕人因為誤解而犯法，反問區議員於心何忍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281256&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281256%26csid%3D261_341&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10P1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=bac61e72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281256&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"61e4c91019894f8f20c516de0047d6c2160d443a","tid":1975314,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"又人血饅頭"},{"pid":"78bd15b967e1e7031e6343119fca1ef642470370","tid":1975314,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"同某啲人口吻一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d443df19bede97890a0755c353c1038f4b5d53","tid":1975314,"uid":283912,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"61e4c91019894f8f20c516de0047d6c2160d443a","tid":1975314,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:35:34.000Z","ms